{"tid":1627834,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（尋人）上水藍絲狗 彩園m記打人","createTime":"2019-10-05T18:10:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T19:01:14.000Z","uid":160534,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"54b2490a1690957469eb7c9d41e00f40a0c4acb8","tid":1627834,"uid":160534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:10:44.000Z","msg":"05.09.2019。17:27 <br />\n上水彩園邨麥當勞，<br />\n一名穿黑衣女子被大陸婆指擾亂香港被打！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zHZtS5H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzHZtS5H.jpg&h=de226d52&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RqPd4cq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRqPd4cq.jpg&h=4cc3af72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSorry 我都知d相曚咗d<br />\n事源係咁 個大陸女人係彩園m記<br />\n同我fd咁啱坐埋一齊<br />\n食食下野就發癲<br />\n話d黑衣人阻住佢地返大陸<br />\n又癈青又曱甴<br />\n咁個女仔fd 就睇唔過眼同佢理論<br />\n只係同佢口角咗幾句<br />\n就比佢鬧曱甴摑到面腫加流鼻血<br />\n<br />\n如果有人見到個經過<br />\n或者識個女人甚至有個住址<br />\n希望可以提供比我<br />\n我想睇下係咪真係大陸人大撚晒"},{"pid":"147c799ff9a6ffae89a1f389ae8f4ff3d82534c2","tid":1627834,"uid":201414,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:12:35.000Z","msg":"成個月之後先拎出嚟講？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a930b367a489756ccad57d0bf2048e235b970670","tid":1627834,"uid":103145,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:12:41.000Z","msg":"今時今日就地正法啦，走咗就好難搵，啲狗更加唔會幫你搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d180fbc16e1e85c17458110a40d166dae4fbe43","tid":1627834,"uid":160534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"147c799ff9a6ffae89a1f389ae8f4ff3d82534c2","tid":1627834,"uid":201414,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:12:35.000Z","msg":"成個月之後先拎出嚟講？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:13:12.000Z","msg":"十月五先岩<br />\n我打錯咗"},{"pid":"6b144e423ac9a12914ccd9